1629
00:57:39,741 --> 00:57:41,441
Are you the one who went past us?

1630
00:57:41,441 --> 00:57:44,441
- Yes. You told me to be careful. - The wheels...

1631
00:57:44,441 --> 00:57:46,511
- Yes, I told you to be careful. - Yes.

1632
